data.title: Ozzy Osbourne > Loudwire
data.meta_description: The notorious “heavy metal madman,” singer Ozzy Osbourne is perhaps the most celebrated and widely recognized artist to ever work in the heavy metal sphere...
data.text:
Britney Spears Tells Osbournes to 'F--k Off' In Response to Diss

Spears penned a long missive about being judged before weighing in on The Osbournes critique of her social media dance videos.

Ozzy Osbourne Names His Ultimate Dream Band

Two guitarists, a bassist and a drummer, but which has played with Ozzy before?

Ozzy Warns Kids About Snorting 'Death Dust' In New Commercial

Comedy commercial comes after customers joked about taking Death Dust like cocaine.

Zakk Wylde Tells His Funniest Ozzy Osbourne Stories

In a new video compilation, Zakk Wylde tells us the funniest stories he has about Ozzy Osbourne, who he's played guitar for on and off since 1987.

These 40 Smiling Rock Stars Will Make Your Day

See photos of smiling rock stars for National Smile Day, including Ozzy Osbourne, Slayer's Tom Araya, Metallica's James Hetfield and more.

How Ozzy Osbourne + Geezer Butler Started Talking Again

Geezer chalks it up to some 'miscommunication' between the musicians and reveals how they've gotten back in touch over the past year.

Ozzy Osbourne Shares His Greatest Fear

During an episode of 'The Osbournes' podcast, Ozzy Osbourne shared what his greatest fear is — rats, and his wife Sharon.

Park Ranger Blasts Legendary Metal Song to Get Bear Out of Tree

Apparently bears find metal music kind of chill when relaxing high up in trees.

Ozzy Osbourne Shares His Biggest Regret About Black Sabbath

Ozzy reveals he's not satisfied with Black Sabbath's legacy and he gives one reason as to why.
